title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 8 2022
description:
Fired-up Virginia mom Merianne Jensen, whose school board speech went viral, talks with C&B. Clay deals with the mindless mask rules in L.A. Erich Schwartzel, author of “Red Carpet: Hollywood, China, and the Global Battle for Cultural Supremacy," talks with C&B about Hollywood's relationship with China.
